---
import "./CardAdvise.css";
---

<article class="round no-elevate p-0 wave">
  <div class="gfx gfx-advise" role="img" aria-label="A radar sweep across concentric rings, suggesting scanning for clarity">
    <span class="ring r1"></span>
    <span class="ring r2"></span>
    <span class="ring r3"></span>
    <span class="sweep"></span>
    <span class="ping"></span>
  </div>
  <div class="p-5">
    <h3 class="mt-2 text-3 lh-2 fw-6">Advise</h3>
    <p class="mt-2 text-1 italic">For enterprises navigating AI at scale.</p>
    <p class="text-0 mt-2">The decisions you make now about AI governance, architecture, and policy will shape what your organization is capable of for years. We help leadership and engineering teams make those decisions with clarity and confidence.</p>
  </div>
</article>
